				\begin{document}$$\begin{aligned} \tau _\nu (\mathbf {x},\mathbf {x}_1) \rightarrow \frac{1}{\lambda _\mathrm{mfp}(\nu )}\Vert \mathbf {x}-\mathbf {x}_1\Vert . \end{aligned}$$\end{document}Equation (49) then becomes a convolution,50Jν(x)=a4π∫d3x1Sν(x1)(x-x1)2e-‖x-x1‖λmfp(ν),\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
